{
  "stem": "23815.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But my husband came first, before me, one year.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We married there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In 19-- 40-- the war-- '46-- 1946, yes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he had a permit, because-- I met him after-- afterwards he had a permit, because the family sent for-- only for him.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then when I married, he came here.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he sent a permit for me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was a year living with them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then I came here to this beautiful country.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Australia was very good to us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I thank Australia with all my heart to give us this opportunity to make a home, a good home.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were wonderful.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It's a-- it's a country that no many countries in the world will give us this opportunity.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] My husband worked very hard.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He was a baker.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "His father was a baker.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "That is for generation.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He was a baker.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he was working very hard.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we did-- things got well.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And then I had two children-- a girl and a boy.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Greta is her name, the oldest one.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And she got two children-- Loni and Troy, and a husband, Ben.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They're all very happy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I'm very happy for them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I'm very proud of them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Harry got three children-- Jarrod, Kiarra, and Tynan.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They are good kids; and Diane, his wife.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I'm really-- I've got a family of my own that I didn't have that before.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I'm so proud.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I'm so happy.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I really am.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "For the first time in my life, I can say I'm really happy.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And my husband died when-- in 1989-- from a heart attack.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "He was a wonderful man-- very clever man.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "He provided us with all the good things that we have today.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "He work hard for this family.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
